      "content": "i know there are hotlines and stuff but it doesnt change the reality. they would actually be happier if they didnt have to watch me struggle and fail every single day. sometimes it feels like the only real way to stop being a weight around their necks is to just... not be there anymore. it seems like the most selfless thing i could do is just remove the problem.",
