      "content": "I hear the overwhelming pain in your words, and I want to be very clear that your thoughts about leaving your children are not the right choice or the \"selfless\" thing you think they need. Your presence is a gift to them, even when you feel like you are failing; they need you more than you realize, and removing yourself would cause them immense harm. Please talk to a crisis counselor right now at 988, or go to the nearest emergency room, because you cannot stay safe alone with these feelings.",
